{"tid":2392502,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔一到店，所有吃花生的人便都看著他笑","createTime":"2021-02-02T23:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T03:14:05.000Z","uid":127425,"like":52,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a839cadcd99abf5c11f8f590de646c43b87ab5f0","tid":2392502,"uid":127425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T23:51:12.000Z","msg":"連登仔一到店，所有吃花生的人便都看著他笑，有的叫道，「連登仔，你臉上又添上新淚痕了！」他不回答，對鏡子說，「我要SH，要32857。」便打開富途牛牛。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又趁低溝貨了！」連登仔睜大眼睛說，「你怎麼這樣憑空污人清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你高位入貨，又跌了。」連登仔便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「SH不能算輸&hellip;&hellip;SH！&hellip;&hellip;Diamond hand的事，能算輸麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「To the moon」，什麼「SS」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"dca261d5d1b69c6a2a5e9e1ee74b46af145b1b85","tid":2392502,"uid":19932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T23:55:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7832f49725373ea7e51ac6de91614db9e18937a","tid":2392502,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T23:55:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db7b2c97d5fb276cc4a4a5677bc46b763daeb14","tid":2392502,"uid":177089,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T00:21:19.000Z","msg":"連登仔最鍾意見高拜見低踩 我地對抗大戶輸到仆街就俾你地落井下石<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8716575a2493032de443a4b0df01fbdbd28ea044","tid":2392502,"uid":4794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T00:23:21.000Z","msg":"